tion of inimitable \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/inimitable\">inimitable</a>。</p><p>它是“形象”的拉丁语源，如 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">imago</i> \"image\"， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">aemulus</i> \"emulous\"， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">imitari</i> \"to copy, portray, imitate; \" 以及“替代”的赫梯语源如 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">himma-</i> \"imitation, substitute\" 等。</p>"
